  <_name>PaintBrush</_name>
  <_summary>Simple painting and drawing application for Linux</_summary>
  <description>
    <_p>
      PaintBrush is a simple yet powerful paint program for Linux, inspired by 
      classic Windows Paint but with modern GTK4 features. Perfect for quick 
      sketches, simple drawings, and basic image editing.
    </_p>
    <_p>Features include:</_p>
    <ul>
      <_li>Multiple drawing tools: brush, eraser, line, rectangle, circle</_li>
      <_li>Adjustable brush sizes and colors</_li>
      <_li>Load and save PNG, JPEG, and GIF images</_li>
      <_li>Clean, intuitive interface</_li>
      <_li>Smooth drawing with Cairo graphics</_li>
    </ul>
  </description>
